   Technology &amp; Health:
   Aequitron Recalls Machines to Monitor
   Respiration and Heart Rates of Infants
   ----
   By Scott Kilman
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/26/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
